WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:04.000
Here are phrases you can use when asking others about their education.

00:05.682 --> 00:06.571
Are you a student?

00:08.365 --> 00:10.265
What do you want to do when you graduate?

00:11.861 --> 00:13.688
How many more years do you have to go?

00:15.362 --> 00:16.595
Which year are you in?

00:18.311 --> 00:19.877
Do you have any exams coming up?

00:21.611 --> 00:22.508
What's your major?

00:24.159 --> 00:25.225
Where do you go to school?

00:27.005 --> 00:28.033
I went to...

00:29.461 --> 00:30.372
What did you study?

00:31.953 --> 00:33.314
I've just graduated.

